      },
      "part_type": "Hadith",
      "path": "/books/man-la-yahduruhu-al-faqih:2:3:5:167",
      "source_url": "https://thaqalayn.net/hadith/34/3/2/110",
      "text": [
        " اَلْحَجِّ خَيْرٌ مِنْ أَلْفِ أَلْفِ دِرْهَمٍ فِي غَيْرِهِ وَ دِرْهَمٌ يَصِلُ إِلَى اَلْإِمَامِ مِثْلُ أَلْفِ أَلْفِ دِرْهَمٍ فِي حَجٍّ»."
      ],
      "translations": {
        "en.bab-ul-qaim-publications": [
          "Hadith.2248 - It has been narrated: \"A dirham spent on Hajj is better than a million dirhams spent elsewhere. And a dirham that reaches the Imam is equivalent to a million dirhams spent on Hajj.\""
        ]
      }
    },
